name: Artificial Imagination #1
description:
This was my first piece of AI art using CLIP & VQGan, and the moment I realised there was something special and truly amazing about this process.

Until this point, AI art never really grabbed me - it was very random and soulless.  But now with text prompts guiding the artistic creation, it puts the artist back in the picture, and the results always feel very human and expressive.

This piece is from a collection of 4 I made using the text prompt 'Artificial Imagination'.

I've been using VQGan from the very first day it was implemented, so I hope this piece represents something historical, as well as my own personal journey and beginnings in this new art movement.
